title: 820-3209 A1466 I/O Board
message:
Hello Everyone, one my customer brought me an A1466 which is 820-3209 board number with a spilled wine problem. Mainboard been cleaned and replaced with the needed parts. But we have some problems on I/O board too which has a 820-3214 board number. Anywhere I can find boardview and schematic for it?

Thanks for your replies.

title: 820-3209 A1466 I/O Board
message: 820-3213 available, similar to 820-3214 but component placement is a little different.

title: 820-3209 A1466 I/O Board
message:
No idea why I didn't see it before on my PC...
